Definition : IS_HOLDABLE_OBJECT(obj)

Defined in : #include <files.h>

Description: Test whether this object is a holdable object, i.e. inherits
             /lib/holdable_item.c (and defines query_holdable_item() )

Arguments  : object obj - the object to test.

Returns    : int 1/0 - if true, then the object is of the requested type.
